+    // driven, no period gate). Kwin's "vblank complete" signal on a
+    // virtual connector IS our pump's grab_pixels ioctl releasing
+    // painter->vblank via evdi_send_vblank() at evdi_painter.c:1185.
+    // Without this throttle, our 500us pump iteration (patch 0020) ACKs
